{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"块级元素","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML（超文本标记语言）中元素大多数都是“块级”元素或<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements\">行内元素</a>。块级元素占据其父元素（容器）的整个水平空间，垂直空间等于其内容高度，因此创建了一个“块”。这篇文章帮助解释这个概念。</p>\n<p>通常浏览器会在块级元素前后另起一个新行。下面的例子表明了块级元素的作用：</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"块级元素示例","title":"块级元素示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This paragraph is a block-level element; its background has been colored to display the paragraph's parent element.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8ABB55<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"CSS\" id=\"frame_block-level_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements/_sample_.block-level_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>块级元素只能出现在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> 元素内。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"块级元素与行内元素","title":"块级元素与行内元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>块级元素与行内元素有几个关键区别：</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"格式\">格式</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>默认情况下，块级元素会新起一行。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"内容模型\">内容模型</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一般块级元素可以包含行内元素和其他块级元素。这种结构上的包含继承区别可以使块级元素创建比行内元素更”大型“的结构。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<p>HTML 标准中块级元素和行内元素的区别至高出现在 4.01 标准中。在 HTML5，这种区别被一个更复杂的<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">内容类别 (en-US)</a>代替。”块级“类别大致相当于 HTML5 中的<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">流内容 (en-US)</a>类别，而”行内“类别相当于 HTML5 中的<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">措辞内容 (en-US)</a>类别，不过除了这两个还有其他类别。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素列表","title":"元素列表","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下是 HTML 中所有的块级元素列表（虽然”块级“在新的 HTML5 元素中没有明确定义）</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"address\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>联系方式信息。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"article\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>文章内容。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"aside\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>伴随内容。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"blockquote\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote\"><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>块引用。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"dd\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>定义列表中定义条目描述。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"div\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>文档分区。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"dl\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>定义列表。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"fieldset\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表单元素分组。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"figcaption\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>图文信息组标题</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"figure\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure\"><code>&lt;figure&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>图文信息组 (参照 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code></a>)。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"footer\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>区段尾或页尾。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"form\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表单。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"h1_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>标题级别 1-6.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"header\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>区段头或页头。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"hgroup\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>标题组。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"hr\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hr\"><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>水平分割线。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"ol\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>有序列表。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"p\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>行。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"pre\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/pre\"><code>&lt;pre&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>预格式化文本。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"section\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一个页面区段。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"table\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表格。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"ul\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>无序列表。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请参阅","title":"另请参阅","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements\">行内元素</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"块级元素示例","id":"块级元素示例"},{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"块级元素与行内元素","id":"块级元素与行内元素"},{"text":"元素列表","id":"元素列表"}],"summary":"HTML（超文本标记语言）中元素大多数都是“块级”元素或行内元素。块级元素占据其父元素（容器）的整个水平空间，垂直空间等于其内容高度，因此创建了一个“块”。这篇文章帮助解释这个概念。","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Block-level elements","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Elementos en bloque","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Éléments de bloc","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ブロックレベル要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"블록 레벨 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Elementos block-level","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Блочные элементы","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"區塊級元素","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/block-level_elements","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/block-level_elements/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements","title":"块级元素"}],"pageTitle":"块级元素 - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}